Giant Weasel
mm 329; Miscellaneous Creatures
dmbr 29
Medium beast, unaligned

Armor Class 13
Hit Points 9 (2d8)
Speed 40 ft.

STR 11 (+0)
DEX 16 (+3)
CON 10 (+0)
